    Elastic Scattering Formulation for Thermal Neutron Scattering   71 1451     
    Analysis," Proceedings of ICNC 2015: 35th International         71 1451     
    Conference on Nuclear Criticality Safety (2015)                 71 1451     
 3. V.F. Sears, "Neutron Scattering Lengths and Cross Sections"     71 1451     
